
Sun Jun  6 17:47:26 CEST 1999

    * Released version 0.13

Sun Jun  5 15:22:15 CEST 1999

    * pgpopts.c: pgpopts_build_argv() documentation enhanced and guessing
      the type of armored data on decryption added.
